Once you've kneaded the dough to a smooth consistency, here's where your fabulous unique imagination will come into play to mold this dough into a beautiful heart. Roll out the pizza to form a circle. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/5/53/Make-a-Heart-Shaped-Pizza-Step-3Bullet1.jpg/v4-460px-Make-a-Heart-Shaped-Pizza-Step-3Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/5/53/Make-a-Heart-Shaped-Pizza-Step-3Bullet1.jpg/v4-759px-Make-a-Heart-Shaped-Pizza-Step-3Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":308,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":508.4065934065934,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
