</p></div>"}

Pinch in the dough at one place to draw it down into the distinct heart shape, with two rounded edges and a dip. Alternatively, use a sharp knife to cut the angle into the dough and remove the dough piece. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/ba/Make-a-Heart-Shaped-Pizza-Step-3Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Make-a-Heart-Shaped-Pizza-Step-3Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/ba/Make-a-Heart-Shaped-Pizza-Step-3Bullet2.jpg/v4-759px-Make-a-Heart-Shaped-Pizza-Step-3Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":308,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":508.4065934065934,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Shape the base to appear pointed, for the end of the heart. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/b5/Make-a-Heart-Shaped-Pizza-Step-3Bullet3.jpg/v4-460px-Make-a-Heart-Shaped-Pizza-Step-3Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/b5/Make-a-Heart-Shaped-Pizza-Step-3Bullet3.jpg/v4-759px-Make-a-Heart-Shaped-Pizza-Step-3Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":308,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":508.4065934065934,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
